          "question": "Under the CIA triad, which component ensures that data cannot be altered without authorization?",
          "options": [
            "Confidentiality - data is kept secret",
            "Integrity - data is accurate, complete, and has not been altered",
            "Availability - data is accessible when needed",
            "Authenticity - user identity is verified"
